>Blocca/Sblocca oggetti</para
></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Meta;<keycap
>=</keycap
></keycombo
></term>
<listitem
><para
>Riduci zoom</para
></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Meta;<keycap
>-</keycap
></keycombo
></term>
<listitem
><para
>Ingrandisci</para
></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Alt;<keycap
>D</keycap
></keycombo
>, <keycap
>N</keycap
></term>
<listitem
><para
>Oggetto successivo</para
></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Alt;<keycap
>D</keycap
></keycombo
>, <keycap
>P</keycap
></term>
<listitem
><para
>Oggetto precedente</para
></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Alt;<keycap
>D</keycap
></keycombo
>, <keycap
>S</keycap
></term>
<listitem
